h1 Confirmed Appearances
hr
div(ng-controller = "AppearancesController as appCtrl")
	div(ng-if = "appCtrl.activeLanDefined")
		em(ng-if = "appCtrl.stillAcceptingRsvps") To get your name on this list or update your status, please fill out the 
			a(ui-sref = "rsvp") RSVP form
			| .
		p(ng-if = "!appCtrl.stillAcceptingRsvps") RSVPs are no longer being accepted. Have fun at LAN!
		h3 {{appCtrl.lanYear}} Attendee Total: {{appCtrl.yesCount}} 
			span(ng-if = "appCtrl.maybeCount > 0") and {{appCtrl.maybeCount}} maybes
		p
			span(ng-repeat = "rsvp in appCtrl.rsvps") {{rsvp.user.firstName}} {{rsvp.user.lastName}}
				span(ng-if = "rsvp.user.primaryHandle && rsvp.user.primaryHandle !== ''")  [{{rsvp.user.primaryHandle}}]
				span(ng-if = "rsvp.guests > 0")  +{{rsvp.guests}}
				span(ng-if = "rsvp.status === 'Maybe'")  (Maybe)
				br
	.empty-table(ng-if = "!appCtrl.activeLanDefined") No previous LAN defined.
